      How this works
    </h2>

    <div class="relative mb-16 flex flex-col items-center">
      <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 mx-auto justify-center items-center md:items-stretch">
        <div class="card-box text-center p-4 lg:p-8 animate-wave max-w-80 sm:max-w-96 md:max-w-80 lg:max-w-96 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat" style="background-image: url('<%= asset_path('card.png') %>');">
          <h3 class="head-med text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#E06540]">Build Stuff</h3>
          <p class="font-['Fredoka',sans-serif] font-normal text-lg" style="color: #333;">
            Websites, games, apps—ship personal coding projects of any kind to earn <span class="italic">shells<image src="/shell.png" class="inline-block w-6 h-6"></image></span>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card-box text-center p-4 lg:p-8 animate-wave max-w-80 sm:max-w-96 md:max-w-80 lg:max-w-96 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat" style="background-image: url('<%= asset_path('card.png') %>'); animation-delay: 2s; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);">
          <h3 class="head-med text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#E06540]">Get Stuff</h3>
          <p class="font-['Fredoka',sans-serif] font-normal text-lg text-[#E06540]">
            Redeem your <span class="">shells<image src="/shell.png" class="inline-block w-6 h-6"></image></span> for Raspberry Pis, Framework Laptops, 3D printers, and dozens of other awesome prizes to power your next project.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="absolute mx-auto md:hidden block left-0">
          <image src="/arc_arrow_top_bottom.png" class="relative max-h-40 sm:max-h-48 -left-4 sm:-left-16 aspect-auto rotate-180"></image>
        </div>

        <div class="absolute mx-auto md:hidden block right-0">
          <image src="/arc_arrow_top_bottom.png" class="relative max-h-40 sm:max-h-48 -right-4 sm:-right-16 aspect-auto"></image>
        </div>

        <div class="absolute mx-auto -top-8 hidden md:block">
          <image src="/arc_arrow_left_right.png" class="max-w-48 aspect-auto"></image>
        </div>

        <div class="absolute mx-auto -bottom-8 hidden md:block">
          <image src="/arc_arrow_left_right.png" class="max-w-48 aspect-auto rotate-180"></image>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-start justify-center mb-8">
      <img src="https://files.catbox.moe/ztikz5.png" class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full shadow-lg mr-4 border-2 border-yellow-300 bg-white">
      <div class="relative max-w-xl">
      <div class="bg-white/90 border border-yellow-200 rounded-2xl px-6 py-4 shadow-md text-left text-[#8B4513] font-['Fredoka',sans-serif] font-normal text-xl opacity-80">
        Building projects?? That sounds like a lot of work!<br>
      </div>
      <svg class="absolute -left-4 top-6" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <polygon points="24,0 0,12 24,24" fill="#fff" fill-opacity="0.9" stroke="#ffe082" stroke-width="1" />
      </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-start justify-center mb-8 flex-row-reverse">
      <img src="https://files.catbox.moe/d3hyls.png" class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full shadow-lg ml-4 border-2 border-yellow-300 bg-white">
      <div class="relative max-w-xl">
      <div class="bg-white/90 border border-yellow-200 rounded-2xl px-6 py-4 shadow-md text-left text-[#8B4513] font-['Fredoka',sans-serif] font-normal text-xl opacity-80">
        Don't sweat it! It is really easy! Let's look at a example!
      </div>
      <svg class="absolute -right-4 top-6" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <polygon points="0,0 24,12 0,24" fill="#fff" fill-opacity="0.9" stroke="#ffe082" stroke-width="1" />
      </svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%= render "example_project" %>

    <div class="flex items-start justify-center mb-8 flex-row-reverse">
      <img src="https://files.catbox.moe/d3hyls.png" class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full shadow-lg ml-4 border-2 border-yellow-300 bg-white">
      <div class="relative max-w-xl">
      <div class="bg-white/90 border border-yellow-200 rounded-2xl px-6 py-4 shadow-md text-left text-[#8B4513] font-['Fredoka',sans-serif] font-normal text-xl opacity-80">
        Oh yeah, prizes! Let's talk about those...
      </div>
      <svg class="absolute -right-4 top-6" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <polygon points="0,0 24,12 0,24" fill="#fff" fill-opacity="0.9" stroke="#ffe082" stroke-width="1" />
      </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section-z py-32 px-4 sm:px-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#97D8F8] via-[#87CEEB] to-[#42A5E7]">
  <div class="max-w-8xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="head-big text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-center mb-4 text-white glow-w">
      Amazing Prizes
    </h2>
    <p class="font-['Fredoka',sans-serif] font-normal text-center text-xl mb-16 text-white opacity-90">
      Redeem these prizes with your tickets! We cover shipping costs, so you can focus on making!<br>
      <span class="glow-y text-[#E7E76B]">All prizes are available while supplies last.</span>
    </p>

    <div class="relative mx-15 md:mx-15 sm:mx-10" data-controller="carousel" data-carousel-row-value="1">
      <div class="slider-box overflow-hidden relative rounded-2xl py-8">
        <div class="carousel-track flex gap-8 md:gap-8 sm:gap-6" data-carousel-target="container">
          <% @prizes.each do |prize| %>
            <div class="carousel-slide flex-none w-50 md:w-50 sm:w-40">
              <div class="prize-card bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl border-2 border-white/30 shadow-lg p-6 md:p-6 sm:p-4 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 hover:scale-105">
                <div class="prize-image w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 rounded-xl bg-yellow-100/20">
                  <% if prize[:image] && prize[:image] != "" %>
                    <%= image_tag prize[:image], alt: prize[:name], class: "w-full h-full object-cover rounded-xl" %>
                  <% else %>
                    <%= image_tag "clubhuman.png", alt: "Prize", class: "w-full h-full object-cover rounded-xl" %>
                  <% end %>
                </div>
                <h3 class="prize-name font-['Fredoka'] font-semibold text-lg md:text-lg sm:text-base text-orange-600 leading-tight m-0"><%= prize[:name] %></h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2"><%= prize[:time] %></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative mx-15 md:mx-15 sm:mx-10" data-controller="carousel" data-carousel-row-value="2">
      <div class="slider-box overflow-hidden relative rounded-2xl">
        <div class="carousel-track-rev flex gap-8 py-4 md:gap-8 sm:gap-6" data-carousel-target="container">
          <% @prizes.each do |prize| %>
            <div class="carousel-slide flex-none w-50 md:w-50 sm:w-40">
              <div class="prize-card bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl border-2 border-white/30 shadow-lg p-6 md:p-6 sm:p-4 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 hover:scale-105">
                <div class="prize-image w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 rounded-xl bg-yellow-100/20">
                  <% if prize[:image] && prize[:image] != "" %>
                    <%= image_tag prize[:image], alt: prize[:name], class: "w-full h-full object-cover rounded-xl" %>
                  <% else %>
                    <%= image_tag "clubhuman.png", alt: "Prize", class: "w-full h-full object-cover rounded-xl" %>
                  <% end %>
                </div>
                <h3 class="prize-name font-['Fredoka'] font-semibold text-lg md:text-lg sm:text-base text-orange-600 leading-tight m-0"><%= prize[:name] %></h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2"><%= prize[:time] %></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

